These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, indie, blues
1. the fan of indie is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the fan of blues##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | juice   |
| Music-Genre      | country    | indie  | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
There 3 different types of food: tomato, asparagus, apple
1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
3. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| Food   | asparagus | tomato | apple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, van, jet-ski
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| Transport       | tram     | van | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, lavender, turquise
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Color   | turquise | white | lavender     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, british, french
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the french##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the indonesian##1
3. the french is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the indonesian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality         | british | indonesian     | french |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, plum, strawberry
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, indian, turkish
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the indian##1
3. the person eating strawberry is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | strawberry | kiwi      | plum  |
| Nationality   | pakistani       | indian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, indian, dutch
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the dutch is on the left of the spanish##1
2. the indian is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Nationality   | dutch      | spanish     | indian    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, peach, pomegranate
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, siglo, montecristo
1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person eating peach is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus | peach      |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | montecristo | siglo |

