.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, puzzles
There 3 different types of food: pepper, kiwi, cucumber
1. the person eating pepper is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | chess  |
| Food     | cucumber     | pepper      | kiwi |

