.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, radish, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, march, may
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating zucchini is in the middle##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | asparagus     | zucchini   | radish     |
| Birthday    | may | march | december |

